name: Tom Holland
summary: The reviews for the new production of Romeo & Juliet starring Tom Holland have been mixed. Some critics have praised Holland's performance, while others have found the production to be underwhelming. The Guardian called the production "a steely cool" and praised Holland's entrance, while The Independent said that Holland's performance fell flat. The Telegraph called the production "a once-in-a generation" and said that Holland was mesmerising, while The Express called it "absolute drivel." Time Out London said that Holland did a "fine job" but that the production was "dark" and "strange." The BBC said that Holland "wows crowds" but that the production was "lifeless." BBC.com said that Holland was not to blame for the production's shortcomings. British Vogue praised Holland's new haircut, while LondonTheatre.co.uk called the production "sexy," "intense," and "haunting." The Daily Mail reported that Holland and his girlfriend Zendaya attended a pre-show event.

name: FA Cup final
summary: The 2024 FA Cup final between Manchester City and Manchester United will be held at Wembley Stadium. The match is scheduled to start at 3:30 pm and will be televised on BBC One and BT Sport 1. Manchester City are the reigning champions, having defeated Watford 6-0 in the 2023 final. Manchester United have won the FA Cup a record 12 times, most recently in 2016. Erik ten Hag, the manager of Manchester United, is under pressure to win the FA Cup as his team has struggled in the Premier League this season. Pep Guardiola, the manager of Manchester City, is looking to win his fifth FA Cup title. Fans of both teams are advised to take separate routes to the stadium as there is expected to be a large crowd.

name: Furiosa
summary: The latest Mad Max prequel, "Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga," has received mixed reviews from critics. The British Film Institute praised the film's "gut-pummelling physicality," while Top Gear noted that it quickly lost steam. SFGATE reported that the film caused a critic to jump out of their seat, but Forbes questioned the presence of an end credits scene. Despite these mixed reactions, Digital Spy reports that "Furiosa" has a strong Rotten Tomatoes rating. The cast of the film includes several stars from the previous "Fury Road" installment, according to RadioTimes. Reviews from Moviejawn and Financial Times have been positive, with both praising Anya Taylor-Joy's performance in the titular role. However, Express revealed that Tom Hardy's cameo appearance as Mad Max has certain limitations. Overall, "Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga" has generated a range of opinions among critics, indicating that it is likely to divide audiences when it is released.

The trailer offers a tantalizing glimpse of Keaton's return as Beetlejuice, while teasing the film's blend of horror, comedy, and supernatural mayhem. name: SRH vs RR
summary: Sunrisers Hyderabad (SRH) emerged victorious over Rajasthan Royals (RR) in the Qualifier 2 match of the Indian Premier League (IPL) 2024. SRH won the match by 36 runs, securing their place in the final against Kolkata Knight Riders (KKR).
